    <div class="whole">
      <secion id="Intro">
      <br><br><br><br> <br><p id="welcome">Welcome to the world of Animal Crossing! Looking for a way to escape the real world? Tom Nook is here to help with the Island Getaway Package. Come adventure on an island where you can kick back and relax while meeting new adorable friends! Unfamiliar with Mr.Nook? Here he is introducing the package to future residents!</p>
      <iframe id="video" width="600" height="320" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WXK3o0f0BnQ" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
      <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>

