  <div class="body">
    <section id="Explanation">
    <h2 id="ex">Where do I start?</h2>
      <img id="nook"src="https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/nintendo/images/5/5d/Animal_Crossing_New_Horizons_-_Tom_Nook.png/revision/latest?cb=20191221043341&path-prefix=en"alt id="Tom Nook">
      <img id="bbs"src="https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/animalcrossing/images/f/ff/NH-character-Timmy_and_Tommy.png/revision/latest?cb=20191228194012" alt id="Timmy & Tommy">
      <br>
     <p id="form2">The first step is to contact Tom Nook to receive this special Getaway Package. Once you get acquainted, his apprentices Timmy & Tommy will help you settle in. Mr.Nook will help you by providing a tent and some other items so you can adjust to the island life. From there on that's where the real fun begins - you can start making the island your custom paradise. You'll be able to share this with friendly neighbors that will cheer you on as you work towards your dream island.</p>
      <br>
     </div>
    <div class="body2">
          <section id="Char">
      <section id="Characters">
        <h2 id="ch">Characters</h2>
        <div class="flex-container">
  <div><img id="isa"src="https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/animalcrossing/images/b/bb/132D65CF-C9EC-467F-A8F5-FD676146AEE1.png/revision/latest?cb=20200610024111"alt id="Isabelle"></div>
  <div><img id="mabel"src="https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/animalcrossing/images/f/fb/Acnl-mabel.png/revision/latest?cb=20140727174432"alt id="Mabel"> <img id="sable" src="https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/animalcrossing/images/a/a8/Sable.png/revision/latest?cb=20130605215854" alt id="Sable"></div>
  <div><img id="blathers"src="https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/animalcrossing/images/b/b3/NH-character-Blathers.png/revision/latest?cb=20200229053519"alt id="Blathers"></div>
</div>
        <div id="info">
          <p id="is">Isabelle is in charge of managing island life and assisting Tom Nook. She will start off every morning with an announcement to update everyone on events.</p>
          <p id="sis">Mabel and Sable are sisters that run the Tailor Shop. Everyday they will have new clothing items and accessories so be sure to check them out!</p>
          <p id="owl"> Blathers runs the Museum where he'll gladly accept donations. He accepts fossils, fish, and bugs - but please be wary of his huge fear of bugs!</p>
    </div>
